  "texts": [
    "Research indicates that divorce or widowhood can lead to negative physical health consequences, with these effects intensifying with age [17].",
    "Other studies have shown, however, that various individuals respond to divorce differently, and negative outcomes may not be pronounced for some people [18].",
    "Additionally, entering a new marriage postdivorce has been associated with improvements in mental health [19].The research on life events and health outcomes is impeded by the lack of systematic representation in electronic health records (EHR) [4].",
    "Natural Language Processing (NLP) emerged as a valuable tool in healthcare for extracting information from clinical notes.",
    "Clinical notes contain unstructured data that can provide insights into patients' social history, including details on mood, medication, lifestyle patterns, and social determinants of health [20][21][22]."
